data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this fully renovated 3BR, 1.5BA residence in prime East Memphis. Immerse yourself in contemporary design, a stylish kitchen, and upgraded amenities. With its prime location, enjoy easy access to the best East Memphis has to offer. This home seamlessly combines comfort and sophistication, offering an open layout, tasteful finishes, and ample space. Whether hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet moments, this property redefines the essence of home.
